channel.title: Uncommon errors when I try to run my server
channel.description:

[code][Launcher] Initing Cache... 0:Dwarf remains 1:Toolkit 2:Cannonball 3:Nulodion's notes 4:Ammo mould 5:Instruction manual 6:Cannon base 8:Cannon stand 10:Cannon barrels 12:Cannon furnace 14:Railing 15:Holy table napkin 16:Magic whistle 17:Grail bell 18:Magic gold feather 19:Holy grail 20:White cog 21:Black cog 22:Blue cog 23:Red cog 24:Rat poison 25:Red vine worm 26:Fishing trophy 27:Fishing pass 28:Insect repellent 29:Tinderbox 30:Bucket of wax 31:Tinderbox 32:Lit black candle 33:Lit candle 34:Lit candle Exception in thread "main" java.lang.RuntimeException: MISSING OPCODE 13 FOR ITE M 35 at com.rs.cache.loaders.ItemDefinitions.readValues(ItemDefinitions.java: 565) at com.rs.cache.loaders.ItemDefinitions.readOpcodeValues(ItemDefinitions .java:577) at com.rs.cache.loaders.ItemDefinitions.loadItemDefinitions(ItemDefiniti ons.java:131) at com.rs.cache.loaders.ItemDefinitions.<init>(ItemDefinitions.java:117)
at com.rs.cache.loaders.ItemDefinitions.getItemDefinitions(ItemDefinitio ns.java:104) at com.rs.cache.loaders.ItemEquipIds.init(ItemEquipIds.java:14) at com.rs.Launcher.main(Launcher.java:66) Press any key to continue . . .[/code]

item.title: Uncommon errors when I try to run my server
item.dc:creator: @Loveandpower Loveandpower
item.description:
@Loveandpower wrote:

you need to go to your itemdefinitions in the server change the readvalues…

make sure to add something like

and then client sided do the same thing by updating the itemdefinitions in the method that relates to it. (a google search told me it’s method1681)
